{"TopicId":193518,"ForumId":16,"TopicTitle":"How can I stop engines from being accounted for in the centre of thrust?","CreatedByName":"Weimaraner","CreatedById":203722,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-05-01T08:58:57Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Weimaraner","CreatedById":203722,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-05-01T08:58:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI was wondering if there is a way me to stop engines from being calculated in the center of thrust, but still calculated in the center of mass to make building VTOLs easier.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"AHHans","CreatedById":197939,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-05-01T09:08:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSet the thrust limiter of the engines to zero. Just don\u0027t forget to set them back. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:cool:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cool.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:cool:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Rhomphaia","CreatedById":2440,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-05-01T09:52:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223778849\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022193518\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221588324080\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022197939\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022AHHans\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n44 minutes ago, AHHans said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSet the thrust limiter of the engines to zero. Just don\u0027t forget to set them back. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:cool:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cool.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:cool:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\